OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Walt Disney's CEO has apologised for   
OL,6, his "painful silence" on a Florida sex 
OL,7, education bill critics warn will       
OL,8, isolate LGBT youth.                    
OL,10,F"You needed me to be a stronger ally in
OL,11,Fthe fight for equal rights and I let   
OL,12,Fyou down. I am sorry," Bob Chapek told 
OL,13,Femployees.                             
OL,15,FHis comments come amid internal        
OL,16,Fcomplaints that "gay affection" is     
OL,17,Froutinely cut from some Disney films.  
OL,19,FThe so-called 'Don't Say Gay' bill is  
OL,20,Fdue to become law.                     
